<html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><title>F3 Midlands</title><link rel="icon" href="/f3midlands/images/f3-logo.png"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/f3midlands/styles.css"></head><body><header class="hero"><nav><img src="/f3midlands/images/f3-logo.png" alt="F3 logo"><div><a href="#aos">Find an AO</a><a href="#new">I'm New</a><a href="#map">Map</a></div></nav><div class="hero-content"><p class="eyebrow">Lexington · Columbia · Lake Murray · Camden · Saluda</p><h1>Free outdoor workouts for men across the Midlands.</h1><p class="lead">No fees. No signup. No excuses. Just show up.</p><div class="cta"><a href="#aos">Find your AO</a><a href="#new" class="ghost">First time?</a></div><div class="stats"><span><b>75+</b> AO listings</span><span><b>5</b> regions</span><span><b>$0</b> always free</span></div></div></header><main><section id="new" class="section split"><div><p class="eyebrow">New to F3?</p><h2>You do not need to be in shape to start.</h2><p>Bring shoes, water, gloves if you have them, and show up ten minutes early. The workout is peer-led, outdoors, and every man is welcome.</p></div><div class="panel"><h3>What to expect</h3><ul><li>Rain or shine</li><li>No one left behind</li><li>Bodyweight, running, rucking, or gear depending on the AO</li><li>Ends with a circle of trust</li></ul></div></section><section class="section video"><div class="section-title"><p>See F3 in action</p><h2>The work starts before sunrise.</h2></div><iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/143444379?title=0&byline=0&portrait=0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen title="F3 Midlands video"></iframe></section><section id="map" class="section map"><div><p class="eyebrow">Map</p><h2>Use F3NearMe to find the closest workout.</h2><p>Open the live map centered near Lexington and adjust the radius to explore the Midlands.</p><a class="mapbtn" href="https://f3near.me/nearby" target="_blank">Open F3NearMe map →</a></div></section><AOExplorer client:load /><section class="section contact"><div class="section-title"><p>Contact</p><h2>Have a question before your first post?</h2></div><form onsubmit="event.preventDefault();this.querySelector('button').textContent='Message ready — send through F3 Midlands contact';"><input placeholder="Name"><input placeholder="Email"><textarea placeholder="Question"></textarea><button>Send message</button></form></section></main><footer>F3 Midlands · Fitness · Fellowship · Faith</footer></body></html>
